{"tid":1628013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"烏煙瘴氣真係被逼戴口罩","createTime":"2019-10-05T20:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:50.000Z","uid":293072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20bb6ebf523e6c72cff77fcf1c29b5c09921a4d9","tid":1628013,"uid":293072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:38:27.000Z","msg":"香港呢排空氣太差，周圍烏煙瘴氣，真係好容易搞到氣管敏感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗保障自己及他人，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[pink]戴返個口罩其實都好合理［/pink]</span>。不過呢個時勢，就算一家三口行落樓散下步，或者出入人多地方都怕被控非法集結/參與暴動，再戴埋口罩又犯多條蒙面法。<br />\n作為一個奉公守法，又有衛生常識嘅良好市民，想問各位巴絲知唔知邊度有<span style=\"color: gold;\">良心醫生</span>可以睇病？我<span style=\"color: red;\">病得咁嚴重</span>真係可能要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎多幾日假</span>，分分鐘<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期二都未返到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>。<br />\n你知啦，香港大把廢青好似我咁體弱多病，相信有好多人都有呢個需要，最好就<span style=\"font-size: large;\">18區都搵到醫生</span>睇症啦。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跪求大家集思廣義，幫小妹解決疑難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ab5f64298b00e237065152c8fa3f13f0c11097b5","tid":1628013,"uid":293072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4862ffdd1ba7c647fc18a517055e5261d63a75bc","tid":1628013,"uid":293072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f4f63d309c5f827429776cf1b7eedeb0ff0ffe06","tid":1628013,"uid":293072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10